title: Spittin' Chiclets Episode 242: Featuring Jordan Binnington
description:
On Thursday’s episode of Spittin’ Chiclets, the guys are joined by Stanley Cup champion and NHL All-Star, Jordan Binnington. Binner joins (1:02:51) to talk about his rise to stardom, playing in the minors, winning the cup, and a ton more. The boys also talk about some NHL news, including the Dustin Byfuglien developments, Blue Jackets, the Devils 20th reunion and a ton more. The guys wrap up talking some Justin Bieber, Oscars and RA gives a Gambling Corner (02:04:31).


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/schiclets
